  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">CT: homogenous fluid attenuating and smoothly marginated lesion abutting the right cardiac border with Hounsfield attenuation unit = 7; Measures 5 x 4.4 x 7 cm</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

