  <title rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Pulmonary Embolism</title>
  <history rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Complains of several days of vague abdominal pain, general weakness and shortness of breath.</history>
  <exam rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Decreased breath sounds to right lower lobe. Elevated ESR.Normocytic anemia.</exam>
