  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">CT scan abdomen: Positive arrowhead sign in appendix. Presence of thickened appendix. Questionable appendicolith. Terminal ileum normal and seen with contrast, Good visualization of ileocecal juntion. Cecum normal size without evidence of edema.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

