  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">CT pulmonary angiogram showing calcificied mediastinal adenopathy with near complete opacificaton of the left main pulmonary artery. There is also dense consolidation of the posterior portion of the left lung seen in the image plane. A chest tube is also seen anteriorly secondary to a prior lung biopsy.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

