  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">A coronal reformatted image from an unenhanced renal stone protocol CT through the kidneys demonstrates calcifications in the renal medullary pyramids bilaterally.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

