  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">More distal obstructing ureterolith with mild hydronephrosis on the left kidney. Incidental note is made of asymmetry of the left psoas size due to atrophy of the left psoas from a previous myositis.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

