  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Axial CT images of the chest show a soft tissue attenuating anterior mediastinal mass with minimal enhancement. The mass insinuates between the vasculature and has convex smooth margins with the lung. No fat or calcium is present.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

