  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Multiple soft tissue attenuated skin nodules noted on anterior chest. No pulmonary nodules or masses seen. Pulmonary fibrosis with honey-combing predominately occurring in the upper lobes. Bullous changes are seen adjacent to mediastinum near azygoesophageal recess. Pulmonary scaring and honey-combing extends to right lower lung.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

