  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Axial CT of abdomen shows shows a markedly thickened (3 mm) and gallbladder wall. The known calculus at the gallbladder neck is not visualized.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

