  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Film 3: Dynamic contrast-enhanced CT image (on liver window) shows a 7 mm obstructed pancreatic duct (arrow) surrounded by contrast-enhanced pancreatic parenchyma seen distal to the pancreatic mass.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

