  <url rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">https://github.com/CHILab1/MedPix-2.0/blob/main/images/MPX2215_synpic48402.png</url>
  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Enhanced CT image demonstrating a trabeculated appearance of the left ventricle with mild wall thickening of the right ventricle. It appears as the right and left ventricle are swapped.</caption>
