  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Nonenhanced sagittal reconstructed CT image demonstrates a well-defined lytic lesion with dystrophic calcifications, sclerotic margin, and mixed areas of fat and fluid attenuation.</caption>
