  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">After contrast infusion, the normal vascular structures enhance brightly, so does the lesion in the left lung.[Labels fromL: Grants Atlas, 10th Edition, Agur AMR and Lee ML, Lipincott Williams and Wilkins, Baltimore, 1999; pg 79</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

