  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">A pulmonary embolus can be seen beyond the bifurcation of the left pulmonary artery as a filling defect with the contrast opacified arterial lumen. Left breast saline implant.</caption>
