  <differential_diagnosis rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Radicular (periapical) cyst--this appearance is fairly characteristic for a radicular cyst, however other considerations include a dentigerous cyst and less likely keratocyst or ameloblastoma.</differential_diagnosis>
