  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Contrast enhanced axial CT through the level of the posterior fossa demonstrates that the patient is status post right suboccipital craniotomy. There is a subtle area of nonenhancing hypoattenuation off-midline to the right, anterior and lateral to the medulla.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

