  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Axial CT of the chest demonstrates a large left sided pleural fluid collection with surrounding enhancing rind consistent with an empyema. Fluid density was 28 Hounsfield units.</caption>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

