  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sagittal T1-weighted MR image shows almost complete disruption of the low-signal-intensity Achilles tendon at a level proximal to the ankle joint with only a few wisps of fibers of the Achilles tendon fibers distal to that point. There is also thickening of the remainder of the proximal Achilles tendon.</caption>
