  <caption rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Axial T2 weighted images demonstrate T2 prolongation within the deep cerebellar white matter, brainstem, cerebral peduncles, and posterior limbs of the internal capsule. A variety of aminoacidopathies/aminoaciduria diseases produce diffuse and symmetric white matter changes.</caption>
