  <title rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Canavan Disease</title>
  <history rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">2 y.o. girl whose parents noted irritability in early neonatal course. This improved by 5 months of age when patient was noted to be hypotonic.She was also diagnosed in infancy with cortical blindness and has developmentally delay. Head size noted to be large.</history>
